item.description:
This will be an "intermediate and up" level meetup. It will be outdoors on a grass field. Intermediate level means: Players with firm understanding of game strategy. Should have a good grasp of skills (passing, setting, hitting) and be able to move around to cover areas of the court. Play should consistently be bump, set, spike.

As always, please remember:

- Respect the RSVP system

- If it looks like you won't be able to make it or will run late please cancel your RSVP in time for someone else to join
item.name: Intermediate Level Volleyball at Greene Rose Heritage Park
